{"title": "Windows Fundamentals", "source": "active-directory", "source_label": "Active Directory", "path": "Active Directory/Windows Fundamentals", "html": "<h2 id=\"remote-access\">Remote Access</h2>\n<h3 id=\"rdp-to-target\">RDP to Target</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>xfreerdp<span class=\"w\"> </span>/v:&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/u:&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/p:&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/dynamic-resolution\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"system-information\">System Information</h2>\n<h3 id=\"os-info-via-wmi-powershell\">OS Info via WMI (PowerShell)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-WmiObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-Class</span> <span class=\"n\">win32_OperatingSystem</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"os-info-via-wmic\">OS Info via WMIC</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>wmic os list brief\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"call-wmi-object-methods\">Call WMI Object Methods</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Invoke-WmiMethod</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"file-system\">File System</h2>\n<h3 id=\"view-all-files-and-directories\">View All Files and Directories</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>dir c:\\ /a\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"display-directory-tree\">Display Directory Tree</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>tree &lt;directory&gt;\ntree c:\\ /f | more\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"view-directory-permissions\">View Directory Permissions</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>icacls &lt;directory&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"grant-user-full-permissions\">Grant User Full Permissions</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>icacls c:\\users /grant &lt;username&gt;:f\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"remove-user-permissions\">Remove User Permissions</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>icacls c:\\users /remove &lt;username&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"services\">Services</h2>\n<h3 id=\"list-running-services\">List Running Services</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-Service</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"powershell\">PowerShell</h2>\n<h3 id=\"view-aliases\">View Aliases</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">get-alias</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"create-new-alias\">Create New Alias</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">New-Alias</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Show-Files&quot;</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-ChildItem</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"view-imported-modules-and-commands\">View Imported Modules and Commands</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">Name</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">ExportedCommands</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">fl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"view-execution-policy\">View Execution Policy</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ExecutionPolicy</span> <span class=\"n\">-List</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"bypass-execution-policy-for-current-session\">Bypass Execution Policy for Current Session</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Set-ExecutionPolicy</span> <span class=\"n\">Bypass</span> <span class=\"n\">-Scope</span> <span class=\"k\">Process</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-help-for-a-command\">Get Help for a Command</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>help &lt;command&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"user-info\">User Info</h2>\n<h3 id=\"view-current-user-sid\">View Current User SID</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>whoami /user\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"registry\">Registry</h2>\n<h3 id=\"query-registry-key\">Query Registry Key</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>reg query &lt;key&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"defender\">Defender</h2>\n<h3 id=\"check-defender-protection-settings\">Check Defender Protection Settings</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-MpComputerStatus</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"windows-server-core\">Windows Server Core</h2>\n<h3 id=\"load-server-configuration-menu\">Load Server Configuration Menu</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sconfig\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Remote Access RDP to Target xfreerdp /v:&lt;target-ip&gt; /u:&lt;username&gt; /p:&lt;password&gt; /dynamic-resolution System Information OS Info via WMI (PowerShell) Get-WmiObject -Class win32_Operati", "tags": []}